            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nIn this text, we will explore, among other topics, knowledge about the relationship of our species with others, as well as the expansion of the Universe.\n\nTherefore, we suggest studying the first chapter of the *Atlas* (<htcite0>), as well as the text about humans (<htcite1>), available on History Tracers, before proceeding.",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "f140d8d6-80cc-4d82-b9f7-c3ba06bf2ed3",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
                     "page": "Atlas",
